author: muscatdaily@apexmedia.co.om (Muscat Daily News)
title: ISC badminton tournament: Prabhu and Niyas bag men’s A title
text:
ISC badminton tournament: Prabhu and Niyas bag men’s A title Prabhu (left) and Niyas October 20, 2015 
Prabhu A R and Niyas N claimed the men’s A doubles title by defeating Cyril Williams and Sudheer Raghavan at the annual badminton tournament, organised by Indian Social Club (ISC) Muscat, on Sunday. 
Prabhu and Niyas won 21-14, 21-12. 
Also, the top-seeded duo of Ronnie and Percy Pereira defeated the second-seeded combination of Francis P T and Saji Abraham to claim the veterans' doubles title. 
Ronny and Persie lost the initiative at the start and were down 17-21 in the opening set, but fought back well to take the next two sets 22-20 and 21-14. 
In the open men’s doubles semifinals, the top-seeded pair of Albert and Haroos defeated Dipu and Geemon 21-18, 21-9. They face Cyril Williams and Sudheer Raghavan in the final. Similar content
